<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Get Involved · Regenerate Skagit</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f8f7f4;
      --text: #1f2933;
      --muted: #5f6c7b;
      --accent: #2f855a;
      --card-bg: #f1f3f0;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
                   "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    main {
      max-width: 42rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    header {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px var(--shadow);
      text-align: center;
    }

    header strong {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    h1 { font-size: 2rem; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    p { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }

    .section { margin-top: 2.5rem; }

    .card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 8px var(--shadow);
    }

    .featured {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 5px var(--shadow);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .featured strong { font-weight: 600; }

    details { margin-top: 1rem; }
    summary {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      cursor: pointer;
      list-style: none;
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    summary::after { content: " +"; }
    details[open] summary::after { content: " −"; }

    .details {
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .divider {
      margin: 3rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    @media(min-width:768px){
      main { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
      h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; }
      h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; }
      h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>

    <!-- Header / Orientation -->
    <header>
      <strong>Regenerate Skagit</strong>
      <h1>Ways to participate</h1>
      <p class="muted">
        Participation looks different for different people, and it can change over time.
      </p>
      <p class="muted">
        What follows describes some of the ways people currently engage.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Participation Cards -->
    <section class="section">

      <!-- Community Gatherings -->
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Community Gatherings</h3>
        <p>Shared meals, conversations, and seasonal events in the Skagit Valley.</p>
        <p>Some gatherings are structured, others are simply time together. Many people start here.</p>

        <div class="featured">
          <strong>Upcoming gathering</strong><br>
          Potluck & Conversation<br>
          March 10 · Evening · Mount Vernon
        </div>

        <details>
          <summary>See how gatherings usually work</summary>
          <p>Gatherings are announced via our mailing list and word of mouth. Some are open; others are smaller and hosted by invitation.</p>
          <p>No expectation to attend regularly. People come when it fits.</p>
        </details>

        <div class="details">
          Showing up when you can · Listening or speaking · No preparation required
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Learning Together -->
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Learning Together</h3>
        <p>Reading groups, workshops, and shared inquiry around land, water, food, and place.</p>
        <p>Learning happens through conversation and attention, not instruction.</p>
        <div class="details">
          Curiosity · Reflection · Learning alongside others
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Supporting Local Projects -->
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Supporting Local Projects</h3>
        <p>Practical ways to support regenerative work already happening in the watershed.</p>
        <p>This may include hands-on help, logistical support, or contributing specific skills.</p>
        <div class="details">
          Seasonal engagement · Clear scope · Participation by availability
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Staying Connected -->
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Staying Connected</h3>
        <p>Some people participate by staying informed over time.</p>
        <p>Occasional updates share reflections, gatherings, and opportunities to engage.</p>
        <div class="details">
          Low volume · Easy to step in and out
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Orientation Reminder -->
    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section>
      <h2>Orientation, not obligation</h2>
      <p>Participation here is invitational. There are no membership requirements or minimum commitments.</p>
      <p>People come and go. Relationships deepen through consistency, not pressure.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <p>Rooted in the Skagit watershed, Cascadia.</p>
      <p>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
        <a href="#">Newsletter</a>
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      </p>
    </footer>

  </main>
</body>
</html>
